<noria:Property/alert_status_critical>
    a noria:Property ;
    rdfs:label "Alert Status Critical Property"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "A property indicating that an alert's severity is critical."@en .

# --- Action Post-Conditions ---

<action_post_condition/interface_restored_confirmation>
